SUMMARY:Durham Bulls Opening Day Social ⚾️ 🎆 🌺 
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nLet’s get out and enjoy a spring n
 ight at the ballpark ⚾🌸\n\nThis meetup is more about the overall hang
  than being a huge baseball fan. Tickets are cheap ($13)\, the park is eas
 y to walk around\, there are good spots to grab a drink\, and it’s a fun
  excuse to be outside\, chat\, and enjoy the opening day energy. There sho
 uld also be fireworks after the game\, which makes it an even better night
  to come out 🎆\n\nWhether you’re into baseball or just looking for a 
 relaxed social outing\, this should be a good one. Come solo or bring a fr
 iend — the vibe is casual\, easygoing\, and welcoming
