SUMMARY:🍻 Beers After Buehler 🌲
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nJoin us Sunday for Beers After Buehl
 er — a laid-back social meetup with a little movement\, a little nature\
 , and a well-earned drink at the end.\n\nWe’ll kick things off with the 
 Al Buehler Trail\, a scenic ~3-mile / 5K loop around the Duke golf course 
 area\, perfect for an easy group walk\, good conversation\, and a little S
 unday reset. The trail loops around the course and nearby woods\, making i
 t a great excuse to get outside before we shift into hangout mode. ￼\n\n
 After the walk\, we’ll make the short stroll over to Bull Durham Bar at 
 the Washington Duke Inn for drinks on the patio\, where you can kick back 
 and enjoy views of the golf course with the group. Think fresh air\, relax
 ed vibes\, and a beer that feels a little more earned than usual. ￼\n\nW
 hat to expect:\n🥾 Casual 3-mile loop\n🍺 Drinks after at Bull Durham 
 Bar\n🌿 Easygoing pace\, social vibe\n⛳ Patio views overlooking the co
 urse\n😎 Good company\, no pressure\n\nCome for the walk\, stay for the 
 patio beers.
